(66, 'Règlement Interieur', 'reglement-interieur', 14, 1, '<p>Le rectorat de l&rsquo;universit&eacute; a &eacute;labor&eacute; un projet de r&egrave;glement int&eacute;rieur qu&rsquo;il met &agrave; la disposition de toute la communaut&eacute; universitaire (enseignants, &eacute;tudiants et travailleurs) pour d&rsquo;&eacute;ventuels enrichissements et commentaires. Toutes les propositions doivent &ecirc;tre envoy&eacute;es &agrave; l&rsquo;une des deux adresses &eacute;lectroniques suivantes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p><span><a href="mailto:reginterieur@gmail.com">reglinterieur@gmail.com</a></span>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<span><a href="mailto:reglementmosta@yahoo.fr">reglementmosta@yahoo.fr</a></span></p>\r\n<p dir="rtl">تضع مديرية جامعة مستغانم في متناول كل الأسرة الجامعية (أساتذة. طلبة و عمال) مشروع النظام الداخلي للجامعة من أجل الإثراء و إبداء الرأي, ترسل الملاحظات و الاقتراحات إلى أحد العنوانين الآتيين</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><a href="mailto:reginterieur@gmail.com">reglinterieur@gmail.com</a></span>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<span><a href="mailto:reglementmosta@yahoo.fr">reglementmosta@yahoo.fr</a></span></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.univ-mosta.dz/images/reglementinterieur/reglementinterieur.pdf">Projet "r&egrave;glement int&eacute;rieur" &agrave; t&eacute;l&eacute;charger</a></p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2014-12-15 00:00:00', 94, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-12-15 08:03:36', 94, '2014-12-04 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 28, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItem