(64, 'Recteur', 'recteur', 14, 1, '<p><img class="size-auto" src="http://univfr.univ-mosta.dz/images/belhakem-1.jpg" alt="" border="0" /></p>\r\n<p>Pr. Mostefa Belhakem</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;N&eacute; &agrave; Frenda en 1963, mari&eacute; et p&egrave;re de 3 enfants, Mostefa Belhakem obtient son Doctorat en chimie-Physique &agrave; Sofia en 1991.</p>\r\n<p>Monsieur Belhakem est professeur et&nbsp; a occup&eacute; plusieurs postes de responsabilit&eacute;s notamment en tant que vice recteur charg&eacute; de la planification en 2002 et vice recteur charg&eacute; de la post-graduation en 2010, il a &eacute;galement &eacute;t&eacute; doyen de la facult&eacute; des sciences et sciences de l''ing&eacute;nieur de 2002-2009.</p>\r\n<p><br />Monsieur Belhakem est Sp&eacute;cialiste en analyse par infrarouge. il a &eacute;t&eacute; membre permanent du comit&eacute; sectoriel permanent &agrave; la direction g&eacute;n&eacute;rale de la recherche scientifique et du d&eacute;veloppement technologique (2009-2011). Il dirige depuis 2007 le laboratoire SEA2M</p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2014-12-15 00:00:00', 94, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-12-16 07:48:21', 94, '2014-12-04 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 5, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 31, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"0","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFon