(76, 'Bourses', 'bourses', 23, 1, '<p><span>L''office national des &oelig;uvres universitaires se porte garant afin de garantir un climat favorable &agrave; l''&eacute;tudiant en lui garantissant un ensemble de services, en comptant sur son r&eacute;seau national constitu&eacute; de directions des &oelig;uvres (DOU) et de r&eacute;sidences universitaires.</span><br /><span>&nbsp;</span><br /><span>Les bourses : Tout &eacute;tudiant inscrit dans une fili&egrave;re de l''enseignement sup&eacute;rieur b&eacute;n&eacute;ficie d''une bourse d''&eacute;tudes universitaire durant tout son cursus fix&eacute;e &agrave; 4050 DA, 3600 DA ou 2700 DA, selon le revenu annuel global des parents, qu''il faudrait fournir chaque trimestre.</span><br /><br /><span>Dossier de bourse :</span><br /><span>1- formulaire des renseignements d&eacute;livr&eacute; par l''administration</span><br /><span>2- Copie du Bac</span><br /><span>3- Copie du certificat de scolarit&eacute; pour l''ann&eacute;e universitaire en cours</span><br /><span>4- extrait d''acte de naissance</span><br /><span>5- Certificat de nationalit&eacute;&nbsp; de l''&eacute;tudiant ou des parents n&eacute; (s) &agrave; l''&eacute;tranger</span><br /><span>6- deux enveloppes timbr&eacute;es libell&eacute;e &agrave; l''adresse de l''&eacute;tudiant</span><br /><span>7- deux photos d''identit&eacute;</span><br /><span>8- Ch&egrave;que barr&eacute; du compte courant de l''&eacute;tudiant</span><br /><span>9- Relev&eacute; des &eacute;moluments du p&egrave;re</span><br /><span>Concernant :</span><br /><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; les parents salari&eacute;s:</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Relev&eacute; du salaire annuel</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Extrait de r&ocirc;les</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Les retrait&eacute;s :</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Relev&eacute; de la pension</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Extrait de roles</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Les commer&ccedil;ants et artisans :</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Bulletin des revenus des commer&ccedil;ants, d&eacute;livr&eacute;s par les&nbsp; services des imp&ocirc;ts&nbsp;</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Extrait de roles d&eacute;pourvu de dettes</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Les non salari&eacute;s et ch&ocirc;meurs :</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Attestation de non activit&eacute; d&eacute;livr&eacute;e par l''APC</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Extrait de roles</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull; Les personnes d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;es ou divorc&eacute;es:</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull;&nbsp; Extrait des actes de&nbsp; d&eacute;c&egrave;s (pour les parents d&eacute;c&eacute;d&eacute;s)</span><br /><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &bull;&nbsp; Certificat de divorce (parents divorc&eacute;s)</span></p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2014-12-16 00:00:00', 94, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-01-15 14:31:39', 94, '2014-12-04 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 41, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"0","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"0","itemCommentsA